{
  "texts": [
    "No significant differences were identified across the control groups, so we pooled them for all subsequent analyses.",
    "Post-treatment measures.",
    "Following the conversations, participants re-rated their belief in the focal conspiracy and then again completed the modified BCTI (α =.92).",
    "Given that, in many cases, participants' focal conspiracies resembled at least one item on the BCTI (the items were chosen to reflect the most popular conspiracy theories), we computed three versions of pre-and post-treatment BCTI scores.",
    "The first version was the mean response on all 15 BCTI items, which we used to identify participants with a highly conspiratorial worldview."
  ]
}